<h1>Installing Java and Eclipse on Windows</h1>

This page tells you how to download Java and Eclipse for Windows.
It is oriented toward Windows XP, but the instructions should work for
Windows Vista as well, except that there will be minor cosmetic
differences in the screen shots and a few changes noted below.  
If you need help, blitz <a
href="mailto:cs5help@cs.dartmouth.edu">cs5help@cs.dartmouth.edu</a>.

<p>

<h2>Downloading and installing Java</h2>

<ul>
  <li> Click the link <a href="http://java.com">http://java.com</a>.
       <p>

  <li> Click on the green button that reads "Free Java Download."
       <p>

  <li> Follow the directions that appear.
  
